Zaujímavé video na CNBC: _h_t_t_p_:_/_/_v_i_d_e_o_._c_n_b_c_._c_o_m_/_g_a_l_l_e_r_y_/_?_v_i_d_e_o_=_3_0_0_0_0_1_5_5_5_4_ 

Čiastočný prepis:

- As you mentioned before the break, one in five respondents has oil going
over $130 a barrel. This is brent crude, we're talking about. A minority has
it going over $150. I participated in the poll. And I submitted a $175
potential price for the third quarter.
- Whoa!
- And I ended up being the high man.
- I've never heard you say $175 before. Brent crude, fine. That means at least
$150 for our West Texas. That's a killer for the economy, John.
- It certainly is. Where that number came from? Is as we're seeing as we
bolted through $110 today, the all-time high for wti, $147. All-time high for
brent, $145. It was different back then. Add 20% to an all-time high gets you
to about $175.
- Where do you get $175?
- From continued tumult in the middle east.
......
- Are we just going to roll up into the $150 range again?
- It looks that way, Larry, absolutely. Technically there's strength in
momentum and strength in terms of the bad news coming out and the dollar keeps
going down.
- If you are right, that is going to really --
- It's not a lock. I don't want to scare anybody. But it's absolutely
plausible for the third quarter.

Voľný preklad:

- Ako si už spomenul pred prestávkou, jeden z päť respondentov očakáva ropu
nad 130 dolárov za barel. To hovoríme o brent crude. Menšina predpokladá 150
dolárov za barel.
- Zúčastnil som sa ankety a dal som $175 možnú cenu pre tretí kvartál.
- Whoa!
- Jeden z najvyšších.
- Nikdy predtým som ťa nepočul riecť 175 dolárov. Brent crude, fajn. To
znamená aspoň 150 dolárov pre našu West Texas [Intermediate]. To je zabiják
pre ekonomiku, John.
- Určite je. A odkiaľ to číslo? Ako sme dnes videli, preleteli sme cez 110
dolárov, najvyššia pre WTI bola 147. Pre brent 145. Vtedy to bolo iné.
Pridajme 20% k maximu a dostaneme $175.
- Z čoho máš tých 175?
- Z pretrvávajúcich problémov na Blízkom východe.
......
- A to len tak znova vylezieme do rozpätia okolo 150 dolárov?
- Vyzerá to tak, Larry, úplne. Technicky je tu sila zotrvačnosti, sila v
zmysle ďalších zlých správ a dolár ďalej padá.
- Ak máš pravdu, potom to naskutku bude --
- Nechcem nikoho strašiť. Ale je to absolútne možné v treťom kvartáli.
